'''后髮座矮星系'''是是[[史隆數位巡天|史隆數位巡天]]在2006年在[[后髮座|后髮座]]發現的一個[[矮橢球星系|矮橢球星系]]<ref name=Belokurov2007>{{Cite journal | last1 = Belokurov | first1 = V. | last2 = Zucker | first2 = D. B. | last3 = Evans | first3 = N. W. | last4 = Kleyna | first4 = J. T. | last5 = Koposov | first5 = S. | last6 = Hodgkin | first6 = S. T. | last7 = Irwin | first7 = M. J. | last8 = Gilmore | first8 = G. |authorlink8 = Gerard F. Gilmore| last9 = Wilkinson | first9 = M. I. | last10 = Fellhauer | doi = 10.1086/509718 | first10 = M. | last11 = Bramich | first11 = D. M. | last12 = Hewett | first12 = P. C. | last13 = Vidrih | first13 = S. | last14 = De Jong | first14 = J. T. A. | last15 = Smith | first15 = J. A. | last16 = Rix | first16 = H. ‐W. | last17 = Bell | first17 = E. F. | last18 = Wyse | first18 = R. F. G. | last19 = Newberg | first19 = H. J. | last20 = Mayeur | first20 = P. A. | last21 = Yanny | first21 = B. | last22 = Rockosi | first22 = C. M. | last23 = Gnedin | first23 = O. Y. | last24 = Schneider | first24 = D. P. | last25 = Beers | first25 = T. C. | last26 = Barentine | first26 = J. C. | last27 = Brewington | first27 = H. | last28 = Brinkmann | first28 = J. | last29 = Harvanek | first29 = M. | last30 = Kleinman | first30 = S. J. | title = Cats and Dogs, Hair and a Hero: A Quintet of New Milky Way Companions | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 654 | issue = 2 | pages = 897 | year = 2007 | pmid =  | pmc = |arxiv = astro-ph/0608448 |bibcode = 2007ApJ...654..897B  }}</ref>。這個星系距離[[太陽|太陽]]大約{{convert|44000|pc|ly}}，並且相對於太陽以98km/s的速度運動<ref name=Belokurov2007/><ref name=Simon2007/>。它被歸類為[[矮橢球星系|矮橢球星系]]（dSph），意味著它有著橢圓的形狀（長短軸之比大約為5：3），[[有效半徑|半光半徑]]約70秒差距<ref name=Belokurov2007/><ref name=Martin2007>{{Cite journal | last1 = Martin | first1 = N. F. | last2 = De Jong | first2 = J. T. A. | last3 = Rix | first3 = H. W. | doi = 10.1086/590336 | title = A Comprehensive Maximum Likelihood Analysis of the Structural Properties of Faint Milky Way Satellites | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 684 | issue = 2 | pages = 1075 | year = 2008 | pmid =  | pmc =| ref =CITEREFMartinDe_JongRix2008|arxiv = 0805.2945 |bibcode = 2008ApJ...684.1075M }}</ref>。

后髮座矮星系是[[銀河系|銀河系]]最小和最黯淡的衛星星系之一{{#tag:ref|只有[[Segue_1|Segue 1]]、[[Segue_2_(矮星系)|Segue 2]]、[[牧夫座II|牧夫座II]]和[[威爾曼1|威爾曼1]]比它黯淡<ref name=Martin2007/>|group=note}} —它的集成發光度大約是[[太陽|太陽]]的{{val|3700}} （絕對[[視星等|視星等]]大約是-4.1），這遠低於大多數[[球狀星團|球狀星團]]的發光度<ref name=Martin2007/>。然而，它的質量大約為120萬太陽質量，對應的[[質光比|質光比]]約為450。如此高的質光比意味著后髮座矮星系主要的組成是[[暗物質|暗物質]]<ref name=Simon2007>{{Cite journal | last1 = Simon | first1 = J. D. | last2 = Geha | first2 = M. | doi = 10.1086/521816 | title = The Kinematics of the Ultra‐faint Milky Way Satellites: Solving the Missing Satellite Problem | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 670 | pages = 313 | year = 2007 | pmid =  | pmc = |arxiv = 0706.0516 |bibcode = 2007ApJ...670..313S }}</ref>。

后髮座矮星系的恆[[星族|恆星族群]]主要是超過120億年以前形成的老年恆星<ref name=Belokurov2007/>。這些老年恆星的[[金屬量|金屬量]]也非常低，約在{{nowrap|<nowiki>[Fe/H]</nowiki> ≈ {{val|-2.53|0.45}}}}，這意味著太陽所含的重元素至少是其350倍<ref name=Kirby2008>{{Cite journal | last1 = Kirby | first1 = E. N. | last2 = Simon | first2 = J. D. | last3 = Geha | first3 = M. | last4 = Guhathakurta | first4 = P. | last5 = Frebel | first5 = A. | title = Uncovering Extremely Metal-Poor Stars in the Milky Way's Ultrafaint Dwarf Spheroidal Satellite Galaxies | doi = 10.1086/592432 | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 685 | pages = L43 | year = 2008 | pmid =  | pmc = |arxiv = 0807.1925 |bibcode = 2008ApJ...685L..43K }}</ref>。后髮座矮星系中的恆星可能是在[[宇宙|宇宙]]中形成的第一批恆星，並且目前在后髮座矮星系中沒有新的[[恆星形成|恆星形成]]。到目前為止的測量都沒有發現[[21公分線|中性氫]] －－意味其上限為太陽質量的46倍<ref name=Grcevich2009>{{Cite journal | last1 = Grcevich | first1 = J. | last2 = Putman | first2 = M. E. | doi = 10.1088/0004-637X/696/1/385 | title = H I in Local Group Dwarf Galaxies and Stripping by the Galactic Halo | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 696 | pages = 385 | year = 2009 | pmid =  | pmc = |arxiv = 0901.4975 |bibcode = 2009ApJ...696..385G }}</ref>。

后髮座矮星系位於和太陽有著相同距離的[[星流場|人馬座星流]]之中，可能是從[[人馬座矮橢球星系|人馬座矮橢球星系]]剝離的恆星組成的。這種關聯性可能顯示后髮座矮星系之前是這個星系的星團或衛星星系<ref name=Belokurov2009>{{cite journal|last=Belokurov|first=V.|author2=Walker, M.G. |author3=Evans, N.W. |title=Segue 2: A Prototype of the Population of Satellites of Satellites|year=2009|journal=Mon. Not. R. Astron. Soc.|volume=397|issue=4|pages=1748–1755|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2966.2009.15106.x
|bibcode=2009MNRAS.397.1748B|arxiv=0903.0818 |display-authors=etal}}</ref>。

